    <title>Gauss&#39;s digamma定理的证明</title>
    <url>/2021/12/22/Gauss&#39;s%20digamma%E5%AE%9A%E7%90%86%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%81%E6%98%8E%20/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<hr>
<p>作为博客的第一篇文章，今天证明digamma函数的一个公式：</p>
<script type="math/tex; mode=display">\displaystyle{\psi \left( \frac{p}{q} \right) =-\gamma -\frac{\pi}{2}\cot \frac{p\pi}{q}-\ln q+\sum_{n=1}^{q-1}{\cos \frac{2np\pi}{q}\ln \left( 2\sin \frac{n\pi}{q} \right)}}</script><p>其中$p,q\in\mathbb{N},0&lt;p&lt;q$.这个公式表明对于任意的在0,1之间的有理数，digamma函数都是有封闭表达的。事实上，这个公式的证明并不是很困难。</p>
<span id="more"></span>
<h3 id="证明"><a href="#证明" class="headerlink" title="证明"></a>证明</h3><p>利用digamma函数的级数表达式：</p>
<script type="math/tex; mode=display">\displaystyle{\psi \left( z \right) =-\gamma +\sum_{n=0}^{\infty}{\left( \frac{1}{n+1}-\frac{1}{z+n} \right)}}</script><p>再利用Abel极限定理，那么</p>
<script type="math/tex; mode=display">\displaystyle{\psi \left( \frac{p}{q} \right) +\gamma =\sum_{n=0}^{\infty}{\left( \frac{1}{n+1}-\frac{q}{p+nq} \right)}=\lim_{t\rightarrow 1^-} \sum_{n=0}^{\infty}{\left( \frac{1}{n+1}-\frac{q}{p+nq} \right) t^{p+nq}}}</script><p>继续化简，得</p>
<script type="math/tex; mode=display">\begin{aligned}
&\quad\sum_{n=0}^{\infty}{\left( \frac{1}{n+1}-\frac{q}{p+nq} \right) t^{p+nq}}
\\&=t^{p-q}\sum_{n=0}^{\infty}{\frac{t^{\left( n+1 \right) q}}{n+1}}-\sum_{n=0}^{\infty}{\frac{qt^{p+nq}}{p+nq}}
\\
&=-t^{p-q}\ln \left( 1-t^q \right) -\sum_{n=0}^{\infty}{\frac{qt^{p+nq}}{p+nq}}
\end{aligned}</script><p>对于第二个级数，需要用到Series multisection：如果函数$f(z)$可以展开为级数：</p>
<script type="math/tex; mode=display">\displaystyle{f\left( z \right) =\sum_{n=0}^{\infty}{a_nz^n}}</script><p>那么有求和公式：</p>
<script type="math/tex; mode=display">\boxed{\displaystyle{\sum_{m=0}^{\infty}{a_{p+qm}z^{p+qm}}=\frac{1}{q}\sum_{k=0}^{q-1}{\omega ^{-kp}f\left( \omega ^kz \right)}}}</script><p>其中$\omega =e^{\frac{2\pi \mathrm{i}}{q}}$.</p>
<p>于是</p>
<script type="math/tex; mode=display">\displaystyle{\sum_{n=0}^{\infty}{\frac{qt^{p+nq}}{p+nq}}=-\sum_{k=0}^{q-1}{\omega ^{-kp}\ln \left( 1-\omega ^kt \right)}}</script><p>所以</p>
<script type="math/tex; mode=display">\begin{aligned}&\sum_{n=0}^{\infty}{\left( \frac{1}{n+1}-\frac{q}{p+nq} \right) t^{p+nq}}
\\
=&-t^{p-q}\ln \left( 1-t^q \right) +\sum_{n=0}^{q-1}{\omega ^{-np}\ln \left( 1-\omega ^nt \right)}
\\
=&-t^{p-q}\ln \frac{1-t^q}{1-t}-\left( t^{p-q}-1 \right) \ln \left( 1-t \right) +\sum_{n=1}^{q-1}{\omega ^{-np}\ln \left( 1-\omega ^nt \right)}
\end{aligned}</script><p>令$t\rightarrow 1^{-}$,那么</p>
<script type="math/tex; mode=display">\displaystyle{\psi \left( \frac{p}{q} \right) =-\gamma -\ln q+\sum_{n=1}^{q-1}{\omega ^{-np}\ln \left( 1-\omega ^n \right)}}</script><p>再用$q-p$替代$p$,得</p>
<script type="math/tex; mode=display">\displaystyle{\psi \left( \frac{q-p}{q} \right) =-\gamma -\ln q+\sum_{n=1}^{q-1}{\omega ^{-n\left( q-p \right)}\ln \left( 1-\omega ^n \right)}}</script><p>两式相加，得</p>
<script type="math/tex; mode=display">\displaystyle{\psi \left( \frac{p}{q} \right) +\psi \left( \frac{q-p}{q} \right) =-2\gamma-2\ln q+2\sum_{n=1}^{q-1}{\cos \left( \frac{2n\pi p}{q} \right) \ln \left( 1-\omega ^n \right)}}</script><p>右式的实部为：</p>
<script type="math/tex; mode=display">\begin{aligned}\mathfrak{R} \left[ \ln \left( 1-\omega ^n \right) \right] &=\frac{1}{2}\ln \left| 1-\omega ^n \right|
\\
&=\frac{1}{2}\ln \left| 1-\cos \frac{2n\pi}{q}+\mathrm{i}\sin \frac{2n\pi}{q} \right|
\\
&=\frac{1}{2}\ln \left[ \left( 1-\cos \frac{2n\pi}{q} \right) ^2+\sin ^2\frac{2n\pi}{q} \right] 
\\
&=\frac{1}{2}\ln \left( 2-2\cos \frac{2n\pi}{q} \right) 
\\
&=\frac{1}{2}\ln \left( 4\sin ^2\frac{n\pi}{q} \right) 
\\
&=\ln \left( 2\sin \frac{n\pi}{q} \right) \end{aligned}</script><p>即</p>
<script type="math/tex; mode=display">\displaystyle{\psi \left( \frac{p}{q} \right) +\psi \left( \frac{q-p}{q} \right) =-2\gamma-2\ln q+2\sum_{n=1}^{q-1}{\cos \left( \frac{2n\pi p}{q} \right) \ln \left( 2\sin \frac{n\pi}{q} \right)}}</script><p>再利用digamma函数的反射公式：</p>
<script type="math/tex; mode=display">\psi \left( x \right) -\psi \left( 1-x \right) =-\pi \cot \pi x</script><p>故</p>
<script type="math/tex; mode=display">\displaystyle{\psi \left( \frac{p}{q} \right) -\psi \left( \frac{q-p}{q} \right) =-\pi \cot \left( \frac{p\pi}{q} \right) }</script><p>于是便证明了</p>
<script type="math/tex; mode=display">\boxed{\color{blue}{\displaystyle{\psi \left( \frac{p}{q} \right) =-\gamma -\frac{\pi}{2}\cot \left( \frac{p\pi}{q} \right) -\ln q+\sum_{n=1}^{q-1}{\cos \left( \frac{2n\pi p}{q} \right) \ln \left( 2\sin \frac{n\pi}{q} \right)}}}}</script><p>有了这个公式，便可以很快的求出一些不那么“显然的”值：</p>
<script type="math/tex; mode=display">\begin{aligned}\psi \left( \frac{2}{5} \right) &=-\gamma -\frac{1}{2}\sqrt{1-\frac{2}{\sqrt{5}}}\pi +\frac{\sqrt{5}\mathrm{arc}\coth \sqrt{5}}{2}-\frac{5\ln 5}{4}
\\
\psi \left( \frac{1}{8} \right) &=-\gamma -\frac{\sqrt{2}+1}{2}\pi -\sqrt{2}\mathrm{arc}\coth \sqrt{2}-4\ln 2
\\
\psi \left( \frac{1}{20} \right) &=-\gamma -\frac{1+\sqrt{5}+\sqrt{5+2\sqrt{5}}}{2}\pi -3\ln 2-\frac{5\ln 5}{4}-\frac{3\sqrt{5}\ln 2}{4}
\\
&\quad+\frac{3\sqrt{5}}{4}\ln \left( 3-\sqrt{5} \right) -\frac{\sqrt{10-2\sqrt{5}}}{2}\ln \left( \sqrt{5-2\sqrt{5}}+\sqrt{5}-1 \right) 
\\
&\quad+\sqrt{\frac{5+\sqrt{5}}{2}}\ln \left( \sqrt{5}+1-\sqrt{5+2\sqrt{5}} \right) \end{aligned}</script>]]></content>
